    "The dataset encompassed data collected from various locations, including Phoenix (AZ), Kirkland (WA), Mountain View (CA), and San Francisco (CA) in the United States, capturing diverse environmental conditions such as 'day and night, dawn and dusk, sun and rain' (Waymo 2019)."
  ]
